<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Compulsory_sterilization&amp;action=edit&amp;section=18" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.healthsystem.virginia.edu/internet/library/historical/eugenics/index.cfm" class="external text" title="http://www.healthsystem.virginia.edu/internet/library/historical/eugenics/index.cfm" rel="nofollow">"Three Generations, No Imbeciles: Virginia, Eugenics, and <i>Buck v. Bell</i>"</a> (USA)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.eugenicsarchive.org/eugenics/" class="external text" title="http://www.eugenicsarchive.org/eugenics/" rel="nofollow">Eugenics Archive</a> (USA)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ushmm.org/museum/exhibit/online/deadlymedicine/" class="external text" title="http://www.ushmm.org/museum/exhibit/online/deadlymedicine/" rel="nofollow">"Deadly Medicine: Creating the Master Race"</a> (United States Holocaust Memorial Museum exhibit) (Germany, USA)</li>
<li><a href="http://home.earthlink.net/~thetabus/eugenics/" class="external text" title="http://home.earthlink.net/~thetabus/eugenics/" rel="nofollow">Eugenics - A Psychiatric Responsibility</a> (History of Eugenics in Germany)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.catholicculture.org/docs/doc_view.cfm?recnum=615" class="external text" title="http://www.catholicculture.org/docs/doc_view.cfm?recnum=615" rel="nofollow">"Sterilization Law in Germany"</a> (includes text of 1933 German law in appendix)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.crin.org/docs/resources/treaties/crc.12/China_CFT2_NGO_Report.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.crin.org/docs/resources/treaties/crc.12/China_CFT2_NGO_Report.pdf" rel="nofollow">"Genocide in Tibet - Children of Despair"</a>(NGO Group for the Convention on the Rights of the Child)</li>
</ul>


